GRE(gre).
Applicant(x) → Person(x).
FinancialAid(x) → ProvidesSupport(ets, x).
EconomicHardship(x) ↔ (Difficulty(x) ∧ (CausedBy(x, HavingTooLittleMoney) ∨ CausedBy(x, HavingTooFewResources))).

Difficulty(x) ∧ CausedBy(x, HavingTooFewResources) → EconomicHardship(x).
